were actually true.

53
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,960
-I heard about another participant.
-Really?

54
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:44,880
How do you think Dong-chan
will overcome this issue?

55
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:47,600
