There's no way out of this.

56
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,240
Let's finish our meeting.

57
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,480
We haven't decided on our final location.

58
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,120
Director Ma.

59
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:13,800
Is the post on
the online bulletin board true?

60
