the cryonics experiment too?

63
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,240
Yes.

64
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,760
You didn't consider anything else
such as her competence,

65
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:35,000
major, or work experience?
