70
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,600
A person who walks a path
that no one else walks,

71
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,440
dreams a dream that no one else dreams,

72
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:56,240
and does things that no one
else ever dares to do.

73
