once it's confirmed.

117
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,160
Okay.

118
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,080
Yes.

119
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,000
Mi-ran, we need to talk.

120
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:46,240
Mi-ran, before we make an announcement,

121
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,160
I need to hear your take on this.

122
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:50,560
What do you think we should do?

123
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:53,720
I'll take care of it.

124
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,600
I'm 44 years old.

125
00:09:57,880 --> 00:10:00,480
Why would I expect someone else
to take care of this?

126
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,680
This isn't something personal.

127
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:06,520
I know you're going through a lot.

128
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,480
You're probably worried about
what I'd say.

129
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:12,480
And you're also worried about
everyone finding out

130
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:15,360
