00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:40,760
(a core member of
the cryonics experiment.)

518
00:32:44,600 --> 00:32:46,640
(Due to the informant's request,)

519
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:48,640
(we had been keeping
this video confidential,)

520
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:51,680
and we also didn't ask the police
for an official investigation.

